Read UK Biobank resource 592 into a named list

Source: R/lookups_and_mappings.R
read_all_lkps_maps.Rd

Reads the UK Biobank code mappings file (all_lkps_maps_v4.xlsx, resource 592) into a named list of data frames.

Usage

read_all_lkps_maps(path = get_ukb_all_lkps_maps())

Arguments

path

Path to all_lkps_maps_v4.xlsx. By default, this is downloaded from the UK Biobank website using get_ukb_all_lkps_maps().

Value

A named list of data frames.

Details

Note: This is a large object (>450 MB)

Examples

read_all_lkps_maps(dummy_all_lkps_maps_path())
